<SLUG> BC-SCIENCE-BRIEFS-DISCOVER-$ADV25-ART-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
BREAKTHROUGH BRIEFS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use Tue., July 25, 2000, or anytime thereafter.) 
 &HT;    
 ATTENTION EDITORS: The following material from The New York Times
Syndicate is for use by DISCOVER NEWS SERVICE clients.
