   IMMIGRANTS-CITIZENSHIP (Washington) _ The Justice Department is
scheduled Monday to release a report on a 3-year investigation of
how the Clinton administration allowed 180,000 immigrants to become
citizens before their criminal background checks had been
completed. By Lizette Alvarez.
</P>
