<P>
   BBN-ARATON-COLUMN (New York) _ Sports of The Times column on the
Reds. New York fans should understand why Barry Larkin vetoed the
trade to the Mets: nearing the end of his All-Star career, he
deserved the right to stay in the town in which he grew up. But the
non-trade that remains baffling is the one involving Ken Griffey.
