<TEXT>
<P>
   Survivor and Big Brother, it has been argued here before, are
not reality shows. They are game shows produced under controlled
and contrived situations.
</P>
<P>
   ``Survivor'' and ``Big Brother,'' it has been argued here
before, are not reality shows. They are game shows produced under
controlled and contrived situations.
