</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ A new book asserts that Americans spend far less time
participating in community life and even hanging out with friends.
Are we placing society's health at risk? By LIZ STEVENS. Story has
moved in ``l'' lifestyle category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
