   THOMPSON-COLUMN &QL;
</P>
<P>
   UNDATED _ The Democrats are having fun ripping Dick Cheney's
congressional voting record and painting the Republican
vice-presidential-nominee-to-be as some sort of snarling right-wing
ideologue. Good for them _ it's always nice to have a little fun
right before you get your clock cleaned. By BILL THOMPSON. Story
has moved in ``k'' commentary category. &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL;
