age-old image of being unfriendly toward minorities in America.
During this election cycle in particular, the party is pushing
African-American candidates in three congressional districts, one
in Georgia, one in Florida and another in New York.
African-Americans active in the party say the GOP serves as a
better match toward traditional, conservative African-American
philosophies.
